NO NO NO - STAY AWAY ! ! !  The staff here is rude.  Dunkin Corp needs to come in and overhaul the manager and staff.  Did not care about the long line, that is expected this time of day.  What is not expected is buying a dozen donuts and being charged extra for certain types.  Also, one person using two registers does not save time.  I calmly and professionally waited in line for my turn.  Please stay with me until I am done.  Do get one of my dozen donuts, wait on someone else, then get my second doughnut, wait on the next guy and then back to me 12 times - that is rude.  The manager's snotty condescending attitude needs to be corrected - If you do not like your job, then leave the company - do not take it out on me.  The negative reviews are correct.  Last time I go here and last time for any Dunkin - Krispy Kreme here I come ! ! !

We won't be going back to this location.
